00:08:03.510 --> 00:08:05.920
ngunit mayroon ding sukdulang sakripisyo.

00:08:08.070 --> 00:08:10.130
Nakita ko na ang parehong sukdulang kasamaan

00:08:11.160 --> 00:08:12.680
